Package: RMVL
Title: Mappable Vector Library for Handling Large Datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Vladimir",
           family = "Dergachev",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "volodya@mindspring.com",
           comment = structure("https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4708-6625", .Names = "ORCID"))
Description: Mappable vector library allows to memory map large datasets on disk. The data is accessed using usual R list and array subscription operators. The data layout is optimized for memory efficiency and vector processing. Simple C API allows for interchange of datasets with outside programs.
